Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The pirates were eliminated?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Their fleet was destroyed, and those who\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}came on board my ship were vaporized.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(640,685,640,630,1690,2200)}They won't let this pass now\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}that blood has been shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,90,,His actions were excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:03.40,Default,,0,0,90,,Commodore, this boy\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}cannot remain here.{ostracise?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.90,Default,,0,0,90,,Shall we hand him over to the pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.20,Default,,0,0,90,,If only that would appease them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:12.20,Default,,0,0,90,,And what if he joins forces with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.76,Default,,0,0,90,,What would you have us do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:16.30,Default,,0,0,90,,Just take his Yunboro and throw him—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,90,,What we should do for now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:23.09,Default,,0,0,90,,is see how the pirates react and find appropriate countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,90,,{\move(640,630,640,685,500,900)}We can deal with the boy later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think he'd go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He was telling the truth\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}about being a soldier in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have asked for his help...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Amy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you for a little something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to detest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have trouble finding\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}logic in their response.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they'd be\N{\alpha&HFF&}..{\r}indebted to me, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying object ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Amy and Bellows!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower your guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for shouting at you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're not mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Bellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She requests that you consume that animal carcass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name's Ledo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you kill all the pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? They are the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but murder is the\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}greatest taboo here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you have no problem with killing and eating animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that we kill\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}and eat fish and birds,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but only enough for us to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't kill unless we have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention,\N the pirates are {\i1}human{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wrong to take lives thoughtlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If killing humans is forbidden,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then why do you arm yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The pirates make others obey them by\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}demonstrating their willingness to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so we arm ourselves to show them\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}we won't go down without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pointing our guns at each other\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}is just a form of negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a saying that goes, "if someone catches\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}fish for you, give them water to drink."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Advocacy for the collectivization of goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't pool our\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}resources, we won't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But the pirates don't\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}play by the same rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We obviously can't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our lives and possessions\N belong to us, not the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a way to show them\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}it's not worth attacking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want them to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But the game's changed now\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}that blood has been spilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll have to claim even more\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}lives to regain their position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, despite what\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}others have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we need your strength\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}to face the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a communicator.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice if you talked\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}with the others too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You still saved me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That bird is my way\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}of saying thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ledo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got nowhere to go,\Nyou could just stay here with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll all get along somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants me to live\N on this ship? Is she serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll consider it.{so japanese}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider it real seriously, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll be going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo, thank you for\N protecting Bellows' ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What a peculiar phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You may go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never really\N liked them to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never thought they'd deride me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, I'm a bit worried\N{\alpha&HFF&}..{\r}about that flying Yunbo—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Marocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Their derision will only\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}increase if you fear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we teach them a lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever secret weapon they have, they're no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Ships at three o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole bunch of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are... pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Worm! We just got word from the freighter Atui.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge pirate fleet has been spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They request emergency\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}permission to join our fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At least thirty pirate\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}ships have congregated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty ships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty much all\N the pirates in the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The crest of the Lobster\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}has been spotted as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The great pirate Rackage...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Their bearings?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They were spotted here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They were seen heading\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}east by southeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We can safely conclude\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}we are their targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll encounter them by the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We should change course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:10:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be pointless.\N We can't outrun them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are thirty\N heavily-armed{guns piled up} pirate ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have fifteen defence ships, and that includes patrol boats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We are severely outmatched!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us attempt negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't leave until\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}the price in blood is paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We should ask for that boy's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Ledo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The pirates are coming our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We will have to fight them tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have already identified\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}the approaching fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am willing to assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wish for my help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore, you should\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}try talking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his fault in the first place that—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider the tactical advantage his Yunboro represents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridget.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ridget.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I speak on behalf of the Commodore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You offered to help us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but are you aware that you're the one to blame for this mess to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I am aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I offer an apology for killing the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In light of your immense firepower,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,would you be able to\N eliminate us as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I could destroy your\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}entire fleet by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why offer to\N help our paltry fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellows told me that you offer water to those who catch fish for you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the pirates ignore this rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I judged that negotiating with you would be more beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.74,runes,,0,0,0,,rebis oueko kartra
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to stay{garrison} here for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your support for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it might be wise\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}to agree to his deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let someone who\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}brought us fish leave thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{halftime}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My job will be to act as a diversion in the upcoming battle. Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:12:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just draw the pirates' attention away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.69,Default,,0,0,90,,Refrain from excessive violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:08.60,Default,,0,0,90,,Your request is understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:12.48,Default,,0,0,90,,I'll try to keep human loss to a minimum.{missing bg line after this (by obnoxious blonde dude)}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So that's what it looks like inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.19,Default,,0,0,90,,Do not enter the cockpit\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:19.06,Default,,0,0,90,,What do you think\N you're doing, metalhead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We know nothing about that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we trust him\N with defending the fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Commodore's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty reasonable, all in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Marocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing from Gargantia yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They noticed us, so it's\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The night is dark; they might\Neven stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's in poor taste, milady!{"in poor taste" for someone kneeling with a grisly beard! Maybe something like "ridiculous," but less reproachful.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The night is our domain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Visual on enemy fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiating battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot that thing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All ships ready to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All ships, commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh look, they actually made the first move in a night battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that Yunboro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's flying all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Get moving! Time to fire back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All ships! Retaliate against\N the enemy fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chezy and the Nephilim got hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chezy is out of commission!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have them retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of the ships should—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Marcus got hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not falter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Additional allied ships have been hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Allied fleet operative period is expected to end in approximately seventeen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm joining the fray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep casualties to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Disable the enemy's weaponry and engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No signs of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crocodile's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grach turned around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Our boys should be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get ready too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lights, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sneak attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Civilians, evacuate to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the Yunboros out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Give 'em some love from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning: mechanized enemy units have infiltrated Gargantia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one\N with a special Yunboroid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Rackage is on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}since I've seen her fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Surfing Lobster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She's heading straight for Gargantia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Target the large incoming Yunboroid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She broke through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rackage crashed into the hull!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's climbing her way up!{"on board" reads like she's already climbing on deck or something}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Send reinforcements to deck one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's coming for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Commodore Fairlock?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to blow his brains out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. It's rude to approach\N a lady from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do like my men aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gung-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Semper fi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You may rule the skies,\N but how will you fare in the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To all enemy personnel:\N surrender immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, Rackage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}did{\i0} warn them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat: surrender immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We guarantee you won't be harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care! It doesn't matter! I'll never—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender. Surrender.\N Surrender immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat: surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Never...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than surrender...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!{cheering}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep hearing that phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an idiom to express gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gratitude, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you intend to deal with the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Chevron would've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My father?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought you dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Th... Tha... Than...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
